linkVariables

public boolean linkVariables(java.lang.String ivar,
                             java.lang.String epath,
                             java.lang.String etype,
                             java.lang.String eport)
Links a client variable with a variable of the External Application

Parameters:
ivar - the name of the client variable
epath - the path of the block
etype - the string 'in', 'out' or 'param' for an input, output or parameter of the block respectively.
eport - the port if the type is an input or output, or the name of the parameter if the type is parameter.
Returns:
true if the client variable exists
